Show up to all meetings scheduled unless given excused absence.
Complete assigned tasks on time.
Participate in small group discussions.
Rotate group representer through group members.
Communicate quickly when stuck.
Use pull requests instead of pushing to prevent mistakes.
Team members will update the Kanban board prior to meeting to keep other members updated.
Any concerns not addressed by team policies should be discussed with Dr. Heroux.

**Team member onboarding**
1. Join Slack Channel
2. Join Github Organization
3. Help teammate learn language that is required

**Team member departure**
1. Leave Slack
2. push final work to github
3. Leave Github organization
